1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 16=

26
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,530
Thanks.

27
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,753
I don't like them undercooked.

28
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:55,480
Thanks. I'm allergic to pollen.

29
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:06,550
Honey,

30
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,600
please get in.

31
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,310
Thanks. You've got the wrong person.

32
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,630
Can you stop turning me down?

33
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,000
I know I used to be awful.

34
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,030
But I will change.

35
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,400
Lu Tingyu,

36
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,680
your wife is Lin Zhi'er,

37
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:21,960
my sister.

38
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:24,030
But we never had real feelings.

39
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,560
She never wanted to marry me.

40
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:26,850
She's always thought

41
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:28,590
this marriage is a cage.

42
00:02:28,926 --> 00:02:30,419
I can sign the divorce papers anytime

43
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:31,360
and set her free.

44
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:32,870
But

45
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,750
I hope you'll stay.

46
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:36,470
As Wen Yan,

47
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,470
accept my love.

48
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:43,270
Tingyu,

49
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,630
I appreciate your kindness.

50
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,710
But this can never happen.

51
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,960
Never?

52
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,310
Why?

53
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,613
Do you still have feelings
for Lu Tingxiao?

54
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:01,750
He and I

55
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,486
ended a long time ago.

56
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:11,800
Lin Zhi'er?

57
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:15,120
Why is she here this late?

58
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,200
Sis,

59
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,160
what brings you here so late?

60
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,630
I found out through Linhai Group files

61
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:33,310
that Lu Jianchuan

62
00:04:33,370 --> 00:04:34,392
and Lin Youqiang forged

63
00:04:34,403 --> 00:04:36,360
a series of documents

64
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,800
for the construction permit.

65
00:04:39,403 --> 00:04:41,169
That's how commercial residences
were built

66
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,790
on the land meant
for cultural tourism.

67
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,000
Oh, my god.

68
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,630
They really went too far.

69
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:47,070
What's your plan?

70
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,760
I'm planning

71
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:51,600
to call a board meeting as the CEO

72
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:54,270
to suspend the Lianxin Island project.

73
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,560
But this affects too many people.

74
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,240
I'm afraid there'll be pushback.

75
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,950
So, I'll use Jin Chanchan's account

76
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,360
to expose all of this

77
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,573
to hit it from both sides.

78
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,240
It must've been hard on you.

79
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,640
Still,

80
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,939
you are the CEO of Linhai Group

81
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,800
and Jin Chanchan.

82
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:13,920
Only you can do this.

83
00:05:14,310 --> 00:05:15,150
(What?)

84
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,360
(She's not Lin Zhi'er.)

85
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,680
(Her name is Wen Yan.)

86
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,120
(She's also Jin Chanchan.)

87
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,040
(The blogger who's gone after)

88
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,630
(both Luzhou Group and Linhai Group.)

89
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:26,630
(The Lu family would never)

90
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,430
(allow a threat like her to stay.)

91
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:31,240
(Once Lu Jianchuan hears this,)

92
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,310
(whether she's Lin Zhi'er or Wen Yan,)

93
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,720
(she'll be out.)

94
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:38,040
(Then I'll become the CEO)

95
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:39,510
(of Linhai Group.)

96
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,270
Oh, right, Qing.

97
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,680
Let's pack up and get ready to move.

98
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,840
Wen Yan is back.

99
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:51,130
Perfect timing.

100
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,310
I bought you some food.

101
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:57,790
Come here.

102
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,070
So much food.

103
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,360
Seeing you safe

104
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,360
puts my mind at ease.

105
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,240
You have no idea.

106
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:10,330
A couple of days ago,

107
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,000
something wild happened to us.

108
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,680
Someone called and said

109
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,830
Wen Yan was kidnapped.

110
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,343
They tried to threaten the boss.

111
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,920
Something like that happened?

112
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,960
Exactly.

113
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,680
They even sent kidnapping photos.

114
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:22,600
They were AI-made, very lifelike.

115
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:23,720
We almost believed it.

116
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:26,000
Good thing I called you then

117
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:27,556
and confirmed Wen Yan was safe.

118
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,490
Otherwise,

119
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:29,830
we would've been cornered by them.

120
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,870
That call was about this?

121
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:34,470
Wait.

122
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,760
You mean

123
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:38,360
you checked with her

124
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,560
that I was safe at the beauty salon?

125
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:42,150
Yeah.

126
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,090
That's right.

127
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,870
Weren't you next door for therapy?

128
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:46,560
I saw you lying there asleep.

129
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,600
I had to leave early after that.

130
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,630
I tried to say goodbye,

131
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,720
but you ignored me.

132
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:52,763
Don't do anything rash.

133
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,630
I want to hear her voice now.

134
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:57,720
Enough. Drop the act.

135
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,070
(Lu Tingxiao)

136
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,800
Don't use such dirty tricks

137
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,670
to threaten me again.

138
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,510
Especially not with her.

139
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:10,040
That kidnapper was ridiculous,

140
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,870
using Wen Yan to threaten the boss.

141
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,070
They have no idea

142
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,480
what price they'll have to pay.

143
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:16,870
Someone should have them all taken in.

144
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,760
They're the villains.

145
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:20,150
Here.

146
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:25,040
Sis, what's wrong?

147
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:38,190
I'm planning to call a board meeting

148
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,400
as the CEO

149
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,070
to suspend the Lianxin Island project.

150
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,430
But this affects too many people.

151
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:46,510
I'm afraid there'll be pushback.

152
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:50,040
So, I'll use Jin Chanchan's account

153
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,310
to expose all of this

154
00:07:51,613 --> 00:07:52,646
to hit it from both sides.

155
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,760
Chairman Lu,

156
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:56,800
you heard her.

157
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:59,070
The one acting as your daughter-in-law

158
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:00,390
and Linhai Group's CEO

159
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:02,040
isn't Lin Zhi'er,

160
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:03,720
but the impostor Wen Yan.

161
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,440
At the same time,

162
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:08,240
she's also Jin Chanchan, the top blogger

163
00:08:08,343 --> 00:08:09,516
always targeting Luzhou Group.

164
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,040
I don't think

165
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,240
she could pull this off alone.

166
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,360
Ridiculous.

167
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,200
What do you think?

168
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,080
Sit.

169
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:32,670
I think

170
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:35,030
Lu Tingxiao is mixed up with her.

171
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,790
He must've known who she was

172
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,080
and kept it from you.

173
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:40,630
He even helped her move up
again and again.

174
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,560
Maybe

175
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:44,750
they've long planned to take your place.

176
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,150
Those two are a real threat.

177
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:53,910
For now, they're still under my control.

178
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:02,270
Of course, I know you control it all.

179
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,840
But

180
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:05,240
as a Lin,

181
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:06,870
I can't just stand by.

182
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:10,080
I hope you'll let me help.

183
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:14,693
What do you want to do?

184
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:24,120
If you help me reclaim the CEO,

185
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,320
I promise

186
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,390
Linhai Group will stand with you.

187
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,030
But to push that impostor out,

188
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:33,630
I need someone powerful behind me,

189
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,840
a man

190
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:39,480
as powerful as you.

191
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,510
You're very smart.

192
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,390
You know who is worth relying on.

193
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:56,590
I definitely

194
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:58,870
won't let you down.

195
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:12,990
Hello, Ms. Xu.

196
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,680
Lin Yuqing,

197
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,910
you really went all in.

198
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:21,270
Ms. Xu, don't say it like that.

199
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:23,440
Things haven't changed.

200
00:10:23,790 --> 00:10:25,200
Back when you were young,

201
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,000
you also took what you wanted.

202
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,120
You're getting older.

203
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:30,480
Go home and retire in peace.

204
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:32,320
Stop blocking younger people's way.

205
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:33,750
You...

206
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:35,510
You're such a sly seductress.

207
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:42,240
I'm planning to call a board meeting

208
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,360
as the CEO

209
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:46,000
to suspend the Lianxin Island project.

210
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,910
I'll use Jin Chanchan's account

211
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,240
to expose all of this

212
00:10:49,433 --> 00:10:50,486
to hit it from both sides.

213
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,270
Jin Chanchan,

214
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,840
since you're set on going against me,

215
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,630
don't blame me for getting ruthless.

216
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,870
Do one more thing for me.

217
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:19,200
Sis, don't walk me out.

218
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:20,320
Hurry back and find him.

219
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,230
I'm leaving.

220
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,690
♪This door♪

221
00:11:56,090 --> 00:12:00,840
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

222
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:04,880
♪With a voice even lighter♪

223
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:07,690
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

224
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,510
♪I know now♪

225
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:14,720
♪What the chill in my body means♪

226
00:12:15,070 --> 00:12:17,940
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

227
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:21,560
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

228
00:12:21,730 --> 00:12:24,720
♪To complete♪

229
00:12:25,180 --> 00:12:28,930
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

230
00:12:29,070 --> 00:12:31,570
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

231
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:35,260
♪Like a door with no key♪

232
00:12:35,570 --> 00:12:37,890
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

233
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:41,470
♪The tears in my eyes♪

234
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:44,730
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

235
00:12:44,730 --> 00:12:46,470
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

236
00:12:46,470 --> 00:12:49,310
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

237
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:51,610
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

238
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:56,090
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

239
00:12:56,470 --> 00:12:58,760
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

240
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:03,430
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
